metadata.instructions:
(1) Spatial distribution data of mountains in China, with the file name of "cn_mountaindistribution.shp", can be opened with ArcMap;
(2) Mountain classification data, with the file name of "cn\mountainclassification.shp", can be opened with ArcMap. And the legend setting file "cn_mountainclassification.lyr" can be viewed in arcmap10.6;
(3) Main mountain ranges data, with the file name "cn_mountainranges.shp", can be opened with ArcMap;
(4) Main mountain peaks data, file name "mainmountianpeaks.shp", can be opened with ArcMap;
(5) Mountain proportion table of the provinces/autonomous regions/municipalities of China, with the file name of "cn_mountainareastatistics.docx", can be opened by office word, etc;
(6)  Contour zoning data of China, with the file name of "cn_contourplane.shp", can be opened with ArcMap;
(7) General situation of mountain formation data, with the file name "cn_mountaintectonicgenesis", can be opened with ArcMap;
(8) Mountain division and zoning data, with the file name of "cn_mountandivisionandzoning.shp", can be opened with ArcMap;
(9) List of main mountain peaks, with the name of "mountanlist.xlsx", which can be opened by Office Excel, etc.
